{"tid":658880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"報道指中興已停售智能手機　台商復供芯片如賜「續命丹」","createTime":"2018-05-09T10:48:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-09T13:44:59.000Z","uid":20058,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"83f86adb11dc0a6545e5bb6e9d39e55f10f80029","tid":658880,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:48:49.000Z","msg":"美國早前宣布所有美國企業或個人7年內禁止向中國企業中興通訊出售零部件。有線新聞報道指，中興可能暫停在內地銷售手機，在北京的官方店亦只剩下少量存貨，內地官網亦已無法下單。《日經新聞》有報道指，中興實際上已停止銷售智能手機。彭博亦引述消息指，中興一筆4.5億美元的貸款已陷入技術性違約，雖已向債權銀行提出豁免，惟銀行尚未回覆是否接受。<br />\n<br />\n中興曾形容美國禁令使之陷入「休克」狀態，然而，《華爾街日報》報道指台灣監管機構已授權台灣聯發科技向中興銷售手機芯片，有如中興的「續命丹」。雖然聯發供應的芯片，未能完全替代美國供應的5G芯片，無法解決中興面臨的所有問題，但仍有助恢復其供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.post852.com/249349/%e3%80%90%e8%b3%aa%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e5%a0%b1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e8%88%88%e5%b7%b2%e5%81%9c%e5%94%ae%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e3%80%80%e5%8f%b0%e5%95%86%e5%be%a9%e4%be%9b/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.post852.com%2F249349%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e8%25b3%25aa%25e6%2598%2593%25e6%2588%25b0%25e3%2580%2591%25e5%25a0%25b1%25e9%2581%2593%25e6%258c%2587%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e8%2588%2588%25e5%25b7%25b2%25e5%2581%259c%25e5%2594%25ae%25e6%2599%25ba%25e8%2583%25bd%25e6%2589%258b%25e6%25a9%259f%25e3%2580%2580%25e5%258f%25b0%25e5%2595%2586%25e5%25be%25a9%25e4%25be%259b%2F&d=phDuAanM8StDKKQ8E6Zu5NtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=bdfed9da\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.post852.com/249349/%e3%80%90%e8%b3%aa%e6%98%93%e6%88%b0%e3%80%91%e5%a0%b1%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e4%b8%ad%e8%88%88%e5%b7%b2%e5%81%9c%e5%94%ae%e6%99%ba%e8%83%bd%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f%e3%80%80%e5%8f%b0%e5%95%86%e5%be%a9%e4%be%9b/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似吊鹽水咁吊住你條命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19baf63e47244588c3c1ebf91137b0d8359ee4e1","tid":658880,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:51:31.000Z","msg":"用mtk晶片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cbd91df87584ac25e2a4353ef0c5156a5c34611","tid":658880,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T10:57:13.000Z","msg":"同南韓乞芯片+台灣on99幫手都無用，仲差好撚多"},{"pid":"493c2ce8c5f64ced197ac97190c4994f840200f8","tid":658880,"uid":52595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:01:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"695d041009144530fe8c6f87af15f0987c475313","tid":658880,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T11:02:17.000Z","msg":"中興既科技人員今日可以黎香港做專才喇"},{"pid":"80c33091d0fb04a76215e26850aea5105012aefa","tid":658880,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-09T13:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}